title: [Baaarnyard Bounty]
description: Colorful barn-shaped lanterns are suspended on high within the bright blue tent, highlighting the gingham-lined wicker baskets affixed to tables in the shape of fence posts.  Wooden shelves are scattered across the silken walls, displaying a variety of rolton artwork crafted from various mediums, the largest shelf balancing a depiction of an armor-clad rolton standing triumphantly above a defeated wolf.  The ground has been scattered with shaggy green cotton rugs, the fringe fraying across planks.
